    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this absolute dream of a car! It\u2019s in such breathtaking, pristine condition that it practically looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I have babied this beauty from day one, and it still has that fresh feel that's so hard to find. It runs perfectly and looks even better in person\u2014honestly, it's a total head-turner! I'm looking for a quick sale, so I've priced it to move. Don't miss out on this gem!",
