    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This 997.2 Carrera S is a collector-grade example of Porsche\u2019s naturally aspirated 3.8L flat-six featuring Direct Fuel Injection (DFI). Mated to a precise 6-speed manual transaxle, the drivetrain is mechanically synchronized to perfection. The chassis is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and a factory-spec limited-slip differential, providing exceptional torsional rigidity and cornering poise. This vehicle has been maintained to an exacting standard, with a clean DME overrev report and a pristine undercarriage free of fluid seepage or oxidation. Every bushing, synchro, and hydraulic line remains in peak operational condition, offering the tactile, analog feedback sought by purists.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
