      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in true showroom condition. Meticulously garage-kept and hand-washed, the exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster without a single stone chip or swirl mark. Step inside to an interior that still carries that new-car aroma; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and free of creases, while every button and electronic feature operates with precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, boasting a documented full-service history and incredibly low mileage. From the pristine engine bay to the spotless undercarriage, it is evident this vehicle has been treated as a prized possession rather than a commuter. Complete with all original keys, manuals, and a clean title, this is the finest example you will find on the market today.",
